        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <article class="article">
          <div class="article__header">
            <div class="article__title">
              Provide inputs and checklists for the participating clubs.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="article__content">
            <div class="o-content">
              <p>
                As we set out to put more emphasis on sustainability topics in
                our league, we want to make sure we create something useful for
                our participating clubs very quickly. A sustainability checklist
                that inspires the clubs to be more aware of their impacts and
                become more sustainable. As our conversations with the leagues
                showed, the degree to which sustainability plays a role in these
                clubs’ strategies varies greatly. Some are already actively
                tackling their impacts, while others are yet to define how they
                want to tackle sustainability related areas of their business.
                We decided to create a checklist to address the most material
                topics and impacts of any sports organisation. Short and
                concise, it should serve as a way for clubs to plan and execute
                their events in the most sustainable fashion.
              </p>
              <p class="text-red">
                <strong
                  >The checklist will be made publicly available on this
                  website.</strong
                >
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
